{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c0392b;\n            --text-color: #ecf0f1;\n            --background-color: #2c3e50;\n            --secondary-color: #34495e;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section#hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.8), rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/c0392b/ffffff?text=Game+Placeholder') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background-color: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.7); /* Overlay for better text readability */\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .game-card h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .game-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .game-card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        a.cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        a.cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e74c3c;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        .social-links a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin: 0 10px;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .social-links a:hover {\n            color: #f1c40f;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Crimson Studios</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Unleash Your Imagination</h2>\n        <p>Crafting immersive worlds and unforgettable gaming experiences.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Crimson Studios is a passionate team dedicated to pushing the boundaries of interactive entertainment. We believe in the power of stories and the joy of exploration. Our focus is on creating high-quality, narrative-driven games that resonate with players long after they've put down the controller.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"games\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Games</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x350/c0392b/ffffff?text=Project+Ember\" alt=\"Project Ember Thumbnail\">\n                <h3>Project Ember</h3>\n                <p>An epic fantasy RPG where players forge their destiny in a world on the brink of war. Explore vast landscapes, master powerful magic, and make choices that shape the fate of nations.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x350/c0392b/ffffff?text=Neon+Rift\" alt=\"Neon Rift Thumbnail\">\n                <h3>Neon Rift</h3>\n                <p>Dive into a retro-futuristic cyberpunk adventure. Hack your way through corporate espionage, uncover conspiracies, and survive the neon-drenched streets of a sprawling metropolis.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>We're always excited to hear from players and potential collaborators.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:contact@crimsonstudios.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"social-links\">\n                <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Facebook\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a>\n                <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Twitter\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a>\n                <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Instagram\"><i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"></i></a>\n                <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Discord\"><i class=\"fab fa-discord\"></i></a>\n            </div>\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <!-- Font Awesome for social icons -->\n    <script src=\"https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}